WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:04.144
In exchange for driving their infrastructure consumption, AWS provides AppsFlyer

00:00:04.144 --> 00:00:08.289
with structured sales acceleration. Consider a stalled deal. What if

00:00:08.289 --> 00:00:12.433
an AWS rep vouched for you? That is the practical

00:00:12.433 --> 00:00:16.578
payoff of this partnership.
